Songtekst van Sevn Alias – "Hoofd Moe"

[Intro: Jay Z]
You, you can be in love with someone, you can love someone, and you not, and if you haven’t experienced love and you don’t understand it and you don’t have the tools to move forward, then you’re gonna have complications, period
